data.description: Welcome to your charming single family oasis! This home is ready to be called your own, with a main level that boasts a spacious living room, a master bedroom, an additional bedroom, a well-appointed cabinet kitchen, and a full bathroom. Need more space? The attic offers two additional bedrooms for your convenience. The full basement is just waiting for your personal touch to transform it into the ultimate entertainment hub. Outside, you'll find a lovely yard with a side driveway leading to a garage. Plus, this home is conveniently located near shopping, dining, and recreation options. Don't wait, make this your dream home today!
